- libgrss-0.5.vapi is generated, after my patches, with:

  vapigen-0.20 --pkg gobject-2.0 --pkg gio-2.0 --pkg libsoup-2.4 --pkg libxml2-2.0 --library libgrss-0.5 /usr/local/share/gir-1.0/Grss-0.5.gir

- libsoup-2.4.vapi is patched with Timm Baedert's patch here:

  https://bugzilla.gnome.org/show_bug.cgi?id=704176

- webkitgtk-3.0.{vapi,deps} is created using the method described here:
  
  http://stackoverflow.com/a/11927072/1132101
  https://mail.gnome.org/archives/vala-list/2011-July/msg00006.html
  
  
